<div><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;"><br /></span></div>
<div><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">How can public universities afford su=
ch obscene compensation? One big reason is that they pay their players noth=
ing. Indeed, while Saban and his ilk enjoy ever-swelling salaries, bonuses,=
